   Project name: Server Pings
   Project description in detail: An App to check the pings to various online game servers. Select the game, location
   (can be detected by gps tracking) and the server you want to ping. The app will constantly ping the server giving you 
   information about the ping time and packet loss. You can use this to decide which server to use to get best experience. 
   You can also use it to detect any spikes in connection while you play. 
